            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-primary-900">Trustworthy AI for EDA</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Engage in discussions on securing AI-generated RTL, protecting sensitive chip design IP, and defending against backdoors, prompt injection, and adversarial attacks in EDA pipelines.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-primary-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
